{"tid":1670861,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［又講大話］陳同佳根本唔係自由身！","createTime":"2019-10-23T07:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T07:17:18.000Z","uid":235118,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f5695f394c1233203ca7e16d4f4582f64c0fca19","tid":1670861,"uid":235118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:04:22.000Z","msg":"港共係咁話陳同佳刑滿出獄，已經係自由身，又係玩語言偽術，宜家仲要係安全屋由警察保護。<br />\n<br />\n實情佢依然係台灣嘅通緝嫌疑犯嚟，宜家台灣派人嚟押佢走，港共唔幫手之餘，仲要收埋佢？<br />\n<br />\n港共話自己係為公義、為曉穎討公道，咁唔該諗返三年前石棺藏屍案，台灣點樣移交疑犯俾香港警察押送。唔該諗下就咁叫個殺人疑犯坐飛機去自首，會唔會危及全機普通市民嘅安危，係唔係應該由台警押送。<br />\n<br />\n淨係掛住自己嘅政治盤算，扺港共俾台灣大大把冚落嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣士林地檢署2018年12月3日正式對陳同佳發佈通緝，並同步發函法務部轉請大陸委員會向香港政府請求遣送犯嫌至臺。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.slc.moj.gov.tw/293537/293550/293551/639560/post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.slc.moj.gov.tw%2F293537%2F293550%2F293551%2F639560%2Fpost&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltlUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=7703e6e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.slc.moj.gov.tw/293537/293550/293551/639560/post</a><br />\n<br />\n轟動全港的荃灣石棺藏屍案更是香港回歸後第一次獲台灣當局「移交」疑犯。<br />\n刑事局將3人拘捕後，並交新北專勤隊看管，遞解出境。3名男疑犯被戴上手銬由台灣特種警察霹靂小組送往桃園機場，乘搭國泰航空CX467航機，轉交香港警方押解返港。其中20名相信是荃灣警區重案組的探員，包了機尾最後4排，3名疑犯則坐在中間座位，兩旁全是探員，附近靠窗走廊兩旁亦坐有探員。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190212/59252329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190212%2F59252329&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2BltlUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=4ebeb7b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190212%2F59252329&h=a002b006\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190212/59252329</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/91Gq2oE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F91Gq2oE.gif&h=16f5b97b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f8EW83H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff8EW83H.png&h=6ee3a9df&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UKnRdvo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUKnRdvo.png&h=6200408f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22a02de7cf246b59729f60b199cd49eee5a46aaf","tid":1670861,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:13:24.000Z","msg":"係佢自己叫黑警保護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08f3abf95944302261cdef7fcb86c97ce8769c5","tid":1670861,"uid":235118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3P9L2sS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3P9L2sS.jpg&h=a0d03c4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58b407a669cdc1de5d242263f30124d149a81813","tid":1670861,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:15:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0bd816d6bd1bb5f791b0e29d45efd2dc39748da2","tid":1670861,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22a02de7cf246b59729f60b199cd49eee5a46aaf","tid":1670861,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:13:24.000Z","msg":"係佢自己叫黑警保護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:17:18.000Z","msg":"如果大家相信中共港共的話<br />\n咁拍片影罪都係自願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}